{"tid":264980,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"慕尼黑1860降班降到去德丙！！","createTime":"2017-05-31T09:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T17:49:58.000Z","uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5302cfef8b67b7345f8b6c1b60b154e83225cdf9","tid":264980,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:38:31.000Z","msg":"德丙用安聯球場咁豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d3a37be0bfdd17529683f51fd15e783229d48c","tid":264980,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:39:33.000Z","msg":"逾6.2萬球迷見證1860降班<br />\n<br />\n1965/1966球季的德甲冠軍慕尼黑1860（TSV 1860 M&uuml;nchen）自2011年Hasan Ismaik成為大股東後一片混亂，今季在德乙只列倒數第3，需與德丙季軍的雷根斯堡（Jahn Regensburg）踢附加賽。<br />\n<br />\n首回合作客和1︰1下，1860今晨返回主場安聯球場有62,200觀眾助威，上半場卻已失掉兩球。至80分鐘部份球迷眼見降班已成定局，把座位拆掉連同雜物擲入草地，更有人欲拆掉圍欄衝入場，令比賽暫停15分鐘才能繼續，騷亂中有10個警員輕傷。最終1860仍以0︰2見負，兩回合計1︰3落敗，自1993年後再次降落第3組別。"},{"pid":"3a992c497061f1a62597b141b8ef2ca19c77f894","tid":264980,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:13:43.000Z","msg":"球迷拆咗球場反而搞到拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c143f6b260805a4b587f74038c649bdc7fcfda39","tid":264980,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:19:40.000Z","msg":"下季拜仁幫下手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1271c8e324722ba768f1727d79d106273a995243","tid":264980,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下季拜仁幫下手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以點幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3a96d25215bc7d24208f7cd5ee63f9803d5ffa","tid":264980,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T14:08:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下季拜仁幫下手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa